Xolile Tshabalala (a mụrụ n'abalị itoolu n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 1977) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na South Africa. Ọ bụ onye a ma ama maka ọrụ ya n'ọtụtụ ihe nkiri telivishọn a ma ama gụnyere 4Play: Sex Tips for Girls, Secrets & Scandals, Blood & Water na Housekeepers.
A mụrụ ya na Vrede, Free State
A na-akpọ ya aha nne nne ya
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na National School of the Arts Theatre na nsọpụrụ yana 'Best Overall Performer'.
N'oge ọ na-agụ akwụkwọ na National school, Xolile nwere ohere igwu egwu n'akụkụ Thembi Mtshali-Jones, ebe ọ ghọrọ onye nduzi ya
Ha rụkọtara ọrụ na egwuregwu The Crucible nke egosiri na Market Theatre
Onye na-eme ihe nkiri ahụ emeela ihe nkiri
O meela ihe nkiri na ọtụtụ ihe nkiri telivishọn dịka , na Soul City oge 7, ebe ọ na-eme nwanne nwanyị Zama
Ọ bụghị naanị na-eme ihe nkiri, Xolile emeela ihe nkiri dị iche iche nke gụnyere "Nwatakịrị Ọzọ".
N'afọ 2002 ọ malitere ọrụ ime ihe nkiri na usoro ihe nkiri telivishọn Generations
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ 'Julia Montene' site n'afọ 2002 ruo 2005, nke ghọrọ ihe a ma ama n'etiti ọha na eze
Mgbe ahụ n'afọ 2007, ọ sonyeere NCIS oge 5 dịka 'Sayda Zuri', na  omume akpọrọ Designated Target
Site na ihe ịga nke ọma n'ọrụ ya, ọ ghọrọ aha a ma ama na mmepụta telivishọn dịka Secret in my Bosom, Scoop Schoombie, Justice for All, Isidingo.
N'afọ 2020, ọ rụrụ ọrụ 'N Job Bhele' na usoro Netflix mbụ Blood & Water
Usoro ahụ ghọrọ otu n'ime usoro ihe nkiri telivishọn kachasị mma na South Africa.
